<section id="services">
  <h1 class="title">Services</h1>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="text-box">
      <h1>LICENSED & INSURED</h1>
      <p>
        A-Grade & Contracting licences produced on request. Public liability
        insurance of $20m. Registered & insured with WorkSafe Victoria.
        Certificate of Electrical Safety provided on completion of work. REC
        22794.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-box">
      <h1>CONSTRUCTION</h1>
      <p>
        New Residential and small commercial. Design & wiring of single or multi
        unit housing, as well as shop and warehouse fit outs. For owners and
        owner-builders who require a personalised service and want the
        contractor on the job. Design, install and liaise with power company for
        temporary and final connection.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-box">
      <h1>MAINTENANCE</h1>
      <p>
        The core of our business! 20 years experience in commercial and
        residential property maintenance, used by many real estate agents,
        property developers and facility managers. From lighting and power
        upgrades in large warehouses, to the single broken switch in your home
        or investment property.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="text-box">
      <h1>HIGH RISK WORK</h1>
      <p>
        Licensed to work at heights exceeding 11 metres. Experienced & confident
        working with scissor and boom lifts both outdoors and indoors amongst
        plant and pallet racks.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-box">
      <h1>EXIT & EMERGENCY LIGHTS</h1>
      <p>
        Periodic testing to meet regulatory requirements and maintain
        compliance. Competitive quotes for repairs on tests done by larger
        companies.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="text-box">
      <h1>DATA CABLING, SPLIT SYSTEM AIR CONDITIONING, SWITCHBOARDS</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

